Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:06.49,Credit,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(2500,0)}Brought U By JPz Records & Masurenai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.05,0:00:12.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard there's a man carrying\Na huge black egg with a doll inside of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.17,0:00:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.18,0:00:18.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, the doll had no arms or legs,\Nbecause there's no way they could fit it inside the egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.99,0:00:20.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.46,0:00:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But since the doll closely resembles a human being,\Nyou would think it could've been a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.33,0:00:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you take a closer look...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:33.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll see that it's neither a doll nor a corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.58,0:00:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a girl with no arms or legs living\Ninside the shell of a black egg.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.83,0:00:43.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If ever you encounter that man, you ought\Nto tell him that you're not the “Girl in the Shell.”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.30,0:00:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}Otherwise, you'll trade places with the girl inside the black shell.
