Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.36,0:00:58.70,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,The man with a “Girl in the Shell...”
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:04.06,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,Such rumor can be heard recently\Nfrom gossips among teenage girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.06,0:01:07.48,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,As a detective, I, Reiji Tokisaka,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.48,0:01:13.34,Default (Thinking),,0000,0000,0000,,was summoned by a former colleague detective Uozumi to a familiar coffee shop.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.36,0:01:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome, Tokisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.31,0:01:28.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uozumi's waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.92,0:01:31.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Reiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.63,0:01:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up and get over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.84,0:01:38.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or I'll get jealous of you two getting all mushy over a cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.67,0:01:40.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut it out. The thought alone gives me goosebumps.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.55,0:01:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The usual, if you may.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.23,0:01:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coming right up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.57,0:01:45.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What were you talking about with Kyouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.03,0:01:47.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just some chitchat.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.96,0:01:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't hitting a move on her, so rest assure.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Idiot! I wasn't asking you about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.99,0:01:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why am I here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.85,0:01:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got another mind-blowing case?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I was thinking if you could lend a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.37,0:02:05.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The case started a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.84,0:02:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We uncovered some severed limbs\Nresembling those of teenage girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.37,0:02:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.56,0:02:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something about multiple mutilated parts of dead teenage girls were sighted in numerous locations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.26,0:02:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tabloids and their authors wrote everything to whatever they please.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.50,0:02:27.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't even confirmed if they're actually dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.67,0:02:30.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For certain, if they are from teenage girls,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.55,0:02:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we can't tell if they're young or old enough to be considered teenagers.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.08,0:02:38.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, that's all the clues we got.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.45,0:02:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However, based from the evidence present,\Nthe police are investigating if this is a case of murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.83,0:02:46.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys did the autopsies, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.23,0:02:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.26,0:02:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's troubling is that there were signs\Nof life before the limbs were severed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.44,0:02:53.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So they were butchered alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.30,0:02:59.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Furthermore, crucial pieces of evidence, the bodies, were yet to be found. Only the arms and legs are kept on site.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.04,0:03:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As of now, the sighted limbs are worth\Nthe total of three teenage girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.36,0:03:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, we have no clues of the victims' identities,\Nlet alone the culprit's objectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:10.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I gotta say that's a mind-blowing case indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.78,0:03:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how about it? Wanna give it a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.09,0:03:16.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can't let a homicidal maniac run loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.72,0:03:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, it just so happened I don't have a case at the moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.21,0:03:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.60,0:03:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so happened you need more info about severed limbs,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.70,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,drop by Takashiro's clinic.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Natsume's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.14,0:03:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand that hag.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The feeling is mutual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:44.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there anyone in the world who doesn't think otherwise about Natsume Takashiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:45.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I doubt it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.93,0:03:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tokisaka, what about your coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.36,0:03:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give it to Uozumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.63,0:03:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll take your offer then.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.43,0:03:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better not involve Tokisaka\Nin anymore of your crazy cases.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.11,0:03:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't work for the police anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.57,0:04:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I get it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.64,0:04:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got something you want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.94,0:04:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems I'm not cut out to be a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.98,0:04:45.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or should I have perhaps expected that\Na detective would notice me tailing him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.68,0:04:47.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Reiji Tokisaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.01,0:04:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.84,0:04:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:55.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You've heard about me from my little sister, Yukari, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That uniform belongs to Ouba Girls Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.30,0:05:03.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus, you faintly smell like my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.48,0:05:08.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To smell like your little sister,\Nwhat a degenerating thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.95,0:05:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.79,0:05:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm talking about the scent of turpentine oil used in oil paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.74,0:05:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's most likely you're in the same fine arts club as my little sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.32,0:05:19.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected from Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.42,0:05:20.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent deductive skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.26,0:05:23.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't call something this trivial deduction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.61,0:05:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.41,0:05:28.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like you've been following me\Never since I came out of the café.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you need me for something?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my, you saw through me as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.13,0:05:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.15,0:05:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose you've passed.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.28,0:05:38.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Touko Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a request.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.59,0:05:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, just a request?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.38,0:05:44.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to find me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:49.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.66,0:05:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real me, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, Mr. Detective...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:56.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka Residence
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.95,0:06:03.48,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H280D04&\bord0.5\fs75\3c&H854228&\b1\pos(916,610)}Tokisaka{\b0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.53,0:06:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home. Dinner's ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.11,0:06:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'll have some.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.33,0:06:11.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're in the fine arts club,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I assume you know a student named Touko Kuchiki, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:17.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Kuchiki?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.36,0:06:19.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why yes, I do know her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But Brother, why exactly do you know her?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kind of bumped into her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:25.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what kind of a girl is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.60,0:06:29.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's kind of unique, in a rather senseless individual is the best I can describe her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.46,0:06:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.40,0:06:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, she is kind of a tomboy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.49,0:06:37.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone in the academy considers her as an odd person as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.00,0:06:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I rarely talk to her,\Nso there's no guarantee to what I say is true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:43.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She knew that I'm a detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.62,0:06:48.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounded like she heard it from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's because your name came to topic\Nwhen I was talking to some friends the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.70,0:06:58.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When I mentioned that you're a detective,\Nshe was sitting next to me and seemed interested.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.94,0:07:02.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She even asked me your name and workplace address.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.90,0:07:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.16,0:07:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to tell the whole world about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.80,0:07:08.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Was that wrong of me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.76,0:07:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought it'd be fine since the academy and the teachers\Nalready know my guardian's name and occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.10,0:07:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.49,0:07:21.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The real me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka Detective Bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.48,0:07:49.07,Signs,,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\fs30\fnBlue Highway\c&H2F2D2A&\move(724,345,633,345,0,1572)}Tokisaka Detective Bureau
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.23,0:07:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.10,0:07:56.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:07:59.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari, good timing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Clean this up for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.11,0:08:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukarin, your bro there?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.17,0:08:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, this place's trashed!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.78,0:08:08.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was quite a greeting,\Nyelling out how trashed this place is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.23,0:08:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.45,0:08:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name's Tsuzuriko Yosomiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukarin's bestfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuzuriko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.07,0:08:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know the Chinese character for “Spell”\Nin English spelling, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.55,0:08:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.19,0:08:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what's used to spell Tsuzuriko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:24.16,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: The name, Tsuzuriko 「綴子」 can also be read Tojiko,\Nwhich means “Clumsy Girl” or plain “Dumbass.”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:22.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, it's Dumbass then?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.66,0:08:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah! That's funny!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.82,0:08:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.09,0:08:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit talking amongst yourselves and changing\Nother people's names without asking!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.51,0:08:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get mad, Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.79,0:08:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit calling me Dumbass!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're already getting along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.39,0:08:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, what business do you and your bestfriend have here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:41.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuzuriko seems interested in detective stuff,\Nso I brought her along.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.72,0:08:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Another one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.13,0:08:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are all the girls in Ouba Girls Academy a bunch of detective maniacs?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.04,0:08:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although Tsuzuriko's just a student,\Nshe writes short articles for people's magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.54,0:08:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's a bookworm girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, isn't that peachy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.24,0:08:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've only been featured in\Nlike three or four magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, in order for my work to hit the spotlight\NI've decided to work on detective genres to spice things up.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.97,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: The Seishi Yokomizo Prize is a literary award.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:10.96,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Note: Kogoro Akechi and Kosuke Kindaichi are\Nfictional detective characters in Yokomizo's works.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:05.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aiming for the Seishi Yokomizo Prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:10.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any dramatic experiences like Akechi and Kindaichi. {Akechi Kogoro and Kindaichi Kosuke, detective characters in Yokomizo's works}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.71,0:09:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reality isn't as interesting as fiction. {lit: novel}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whatever!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.90,0:09:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my job to make it interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.35,0:09:25.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I want you to scoop some\Nrealistic aspect as a reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:27.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's about what detectives do, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:29.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's about cleaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.05,0:09:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jotting, jotting...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.75,0:09:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Detective work is about clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.23,0:09:32.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait-
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.90,0:09:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.51,0:09:34.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.40,0:09:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Having one more will do the job faster.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.71,0:09:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cleaning has nothing to do with detective work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.10,0:09:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Brother, do you have a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.15,0:09:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got something else better to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.76,0:09:45.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll help clean...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.65,0:09:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.73,0:09:48.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something I have to ask beforehand.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.00,0:09:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.18,0:09:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be going to the art museum this coming Sunday.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you chaperon for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Art museum?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:56.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.75,0:09:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There'll be holding an exhibit on Shinzou Mamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:03.36,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Notebook Title: “Case 42”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.15,0:10:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fine arts club members were discussing\Non how we're going to attend, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.07,0:10:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's an off-campus activities on holidays,\Nwe need a chaperon to attend with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:11.38,Note,,0000,0000,0000,,Notebook Title: “Case Report”
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.37,0:10:09.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.37,0:10:11.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got it. I'm free this Sunday, so I'll tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.12,0:10:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.37,0:10:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, let's wrap it up, Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.75,0:10:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.29,0:10:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wrap it up?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.33,0:10:19.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.01,0:10:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you just call me Dumbass a second ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.37,0:10:21.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.46,0:10:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let it go, Dumbass.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.79,0:10:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you're my bestfriend, you'll help out, right, Dumbass?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.88,0:10:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you did call me Dumbass!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.01,0:10:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez! Yukarin, quit calling me Dumbass!!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.58,0:10:43.97,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: OPEN
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.46,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Sign: CLOSED
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.96,0:10:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, closing the shop already?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.08,0:10:47.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.75,0:10:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There weren't any customers today,\Nso I've decided to close the café early.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.41,0:10:54.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's okay. Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.29,0:10:59.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.81,0:11:02.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't gotten over Yukiko yet, have you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.93,0:11:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.15,0:11:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel the same as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Death of a loved one is the worst way to say farewell.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.69,0:11:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a widow, but still so young.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.72,0:11:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should wrap it up and make a fresh new start.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.87,0:11:21.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka, I don't think you're one to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.97,0:11:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us is ready to find a new love life,\Nbut there are times when one gets lonely, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.65,0:11:32.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.57,0:11:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're actually going to console me,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.42,0:11:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,800)}then words alone won't be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure about this, Kyouko?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.36,0:12:07.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.37,0:12:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind if this is a relationship\Nwhere we soothe each other's pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.09,0:12:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.67,0:12:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, this will keep us from being lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.85,0:14:02.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.00,0:14:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.74,0:14:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so gentle...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.42,0:14:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I want you to drive me wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.85,0:14:33.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.55,0:14:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.07,0:14:38.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.63,0:14:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't felt this hot for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:44.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... can feel it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.26,0:14:48.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like I'm about to cum from being embraced by a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:52.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me too, Kyouko...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.21,0:14:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've almost forgotten how it felt to be inside a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.61,0:14:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka-kun, do me harder!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.42,0:15:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.88,0:15:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokisaka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.73,0:15:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is Tokisaka's...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.53,0:15:26.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyouko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.77,0:15:29.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't think I can add this in the menu, can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.58,0:15:30.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, duh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.88,0:15:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.64,0:15:37.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}If Uozumi knew about this, he'd probably kill me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.71,0:15:44.66,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinzou Mamiya Exhibit
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.82,0:15:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.87,0:15:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We meet again, Mr. Detective.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.99,0:15:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a coincidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:57.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hi, Miss Kuchiki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.25,0:15:59.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just call me, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.64,0:16:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're friends after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.06,0:16:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, hey, don't jump on the boat just yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.53,0:16:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.82,0:16:12.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.57,0:16:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.30,0:16:17.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Tokisaka's older brother, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.79,0:16:19.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.05,0:16:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's my bestfriend, Touko Mizuhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.94,0:16:25.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Coincidently, we have the same name.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.85,0:16:27.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-It definitely not a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.02,0:16:31.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's fate that brought us together!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.76,0:16:33.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think the same way too, Touko?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.27,0:16:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.52,0:16:38.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,People always meet each other for a reason...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.41,0:16:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least, I think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.21,0:16:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway! Touko, you shouldn't speak with men!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.95,0:16:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.02,0:16:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My, my...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.57,0:16:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Teenage girls nowadays are so out of this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.00,0:17:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.51,0:17:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, she looks exactly like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.89,0:17:23.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Touko, did you model for this one?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.78,0:17:25.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.93,0:17:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, she really looks like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.14,0:17:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to disappoint you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.32,0:17:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That portrait “Girl in the Shell” was painted\Na decade before the end of the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.18,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really were the model for this painting,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you would look exactly the same\Nten years ago as you do now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.53,0:17:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If so, then that means you'd possess eternal youth like the “Girl in the Shell.”
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.82,0:18:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No smoking within the art museum.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:01.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, my bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.21,0:18:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was just bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.21,0:18:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're surrounded by so many wonderful pieces of art here.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.40,0:18:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I find it strange that you're bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.33,0:18:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.28,0:18:11.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not really into paintings.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.96,0:18:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This piece was painted by Shinzou Mamiya before the war.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.73,0:18:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Although the brushwork he used was technically simple,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.96,0:18:22.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,his bold color scheming proved favorable\Nto even people overseas.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.44,0:18:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.53,0:18:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And this piece of here was painted\Nafter the war at Hiroshima.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.00,0:18:35.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, he painted this over several months\Nwhile observing on what's left by the atomic bomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.05,0:18:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You sure know a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Stella's job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.43,0:18:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Stella your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.48,0:18:47.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This exhibit showcases Shinzou Mamiya's\Npieces under the theme of “Rebirth.”
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.27,0:18:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Using religion as an inspiration to his work, his pieces\Nwere exhibited in Osaka and Kurashiki Art Museums.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By then, Mamiya created his own series of\Nreligiously inspired paintings about death and rebirth.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.24,0:19:04.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've met before, have we, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.52,0:19:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have these paintings drawn to your taste?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.51,0:19:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, have you been coming here lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.04,0:19:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You could have invited me to come tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.01,0:19:14.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you come here without me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.97,0:19:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You also could have told me that\Nthere were wonderful paintings here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.70,0:19:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Touko, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.07,0:19:23.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, Touko.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.88,0:19:30.31,Episode,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinzou Mamiya Exhibit
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.89,0:19:39.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're acting as the chaperon for the students today,\Nso please refrain from smoking.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:42.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What, you too?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.35,0:19:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, are you girls attending a rich and prestigious academy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.39,0:19:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you girls even afford someone\Nbetter than me as chaperon for the holiday?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no helping it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, many students have gone\Nmissing one after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.24,0:19:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even the teachers advised us to stay indoors as much as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.34,0:19:59.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.42,0:20:00.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First time hearing that in my book.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It is possible that the students ran away from home\Nand the academy hasn't reported it to the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did the first student gone missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.88,0:20:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm unsure, but probably about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.65,0:20:14.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many have gone missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:16.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Three students...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.52,0:20:18.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.65,0:20:21.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:22.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yukari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you get a hold of the personal belongings\Nof the missing students?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.81,0:20:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything that might have their fingerprints?
